    "name": "James Grant",
    "profile": "[b]NOT TO CONFUSE with London-based [a=James Grant (4)], A&R and co-founder of label [l=Anjunadeep].[/b]\r\n\r\nJames Grant's music career began in 1982 as songwriter and guitarist in [a=Friends Again]. When they split in 1985 he formed [a=Love And Money] and split in 1994. During this time they released four albums. They reformed in 2011.\r\nHe then went solo and has released 5 studio albums and has scored the film The Near Room and collaborated with [a=Karen Matheson] on her solo albums. ",
